node.text:
Drastic transformation and reconfiguration on this master bathroom project in Ottawa Hills, OH. It was a unique challenge building a massive custom pan for the wet room to keep the tub level and pitch everything else towards a linear drain under the shower fixtures. Always a pleasure working with Donald MacKinnon on the design and thanks to our customer for bringing us in on your project!

Via @huffmansarver1
